<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="go-down">go down</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>下去：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let's go down by lift.
我们乘电梯下去吧。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-sink-set">2.★ <strong>(船等) 下沉 (sink)；(日、月等) 落下 (set)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ship went down by 12 feet.
船下沉了12英尺。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After a long day of study, he likes to watch the sun go down and wait for the stars to come out.
一整天的学习后，他喜欢看着太阳落山，等待星星出来。</p><footer>人教新必修① – Welcome Unit</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>(风、海面等) 平静下来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The wind / sea is going down.
风在平息/海潮在下降。</p></div>

<h4 id="4-fall">4.★ <strong>(价格、数量等) 下降 (fall)</strong></h4>
<p>反 go up </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sales of watches to young adults have been going down since 2007.
自2007年以来，青壮年手表的销售额一直在下降。</p><footer>2008 湖北</footer></div></div>